<DOCOLDNO>IA007-000070-B009-232</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/euforic/dandc/96e_ash.htm 193.128.6.150 19970222022752 text/html 32989
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
