<html>
<head>
<title>So you want to work overseas with VSO? </title>
<!!keys: >
</head>
<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<hr>
<h2> VSO volunteers are flexible, adaptable individuals.</h2>


They earn a modest living allowance which enables them to maintain a similar lifestyle to their colleagues overseas.  That's not to say you wouldn't kill for a slice of marmite on toast but it is going to  be a rare luxury rather than an everyday occurrence.  You will have enough money to live reasonably whilst overseas.  
