Save the Children

<br clear=right>

<H1>Question numero uno</H1>

<H3>See that pair of jeans? They cost, rivets and all, at your denim-filled high street shop, a mere 24 quid. Bargain. How much of that goes to the producer of the cotton that they are made from?</H3>

<UL TYPE=SQUARE>

<LI>60 measly pence?

<LI>A barely decent six quid?

<LI>A very handsome sixteen smackers?

</UL>

