<HEAD><TITLE>Answer one</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff">

Save the Children

<br clear=right><H2>The answer is ....60 pence</H2>

<P>Ho ho, congratulations if you got it right. And congratulations if you didn't - because that shows you are a nice personage with a serious sense of fairness. Trouble is the producers tend to live in the poorest parts of the world. And they don't have much bargaining power.</P>

