<hr>
<h2>Both</h2>


VSO is an international development agency, sending volunteers to share their skills with other people so they can make their own way in the world. Being a volunteer isn't backpacking. It's usually a two year commitment to living and working in the local community. Volunteers are professional individuals with an ability to pass on their skills to others.
