<TD>9.00</TD><TD>9.00</TD><TD>28.80</TD>

</TR>

<TR>

<TD>Pr&ecirc;ts de la BEI: capitaux &agrave; risques</TD><TD>-</TD><TD>3.30</TD><TD>4.20</TD><TD>1.50</TD><TD>9.00</td>

</TR>



<TR>

<td>Stabex</TD><TD>2.80</TD><TD>6.50</TD><TD>11.10</TD><TD>5.70</TD><TD>26.10</td>

</TR>



<TR>

<td>Autres, aide d'urgence</TD><TD>-</TD><TD>0.14</TD><TD>0.20</TD><TD>0.30</TD><TD>0.64</td>

</TR>



<TR>

<td><b>Total</TD><TD>7.40</TD><TD>16.14</TD><TD>24.50</TD><TD>16.50</TD><TD>64.54</td>

</TR>

</TABLE></center>





<P>

<hr>

