(Copies of the report can be obtained from Laura Kelly, ACTIONAID,

Hamlyn House, Macdonald Road, Archway, London N19 5PG, UK) </FONT>

<P>

<FONT SIZE=2>Tel. +171 2821 4101, Fax. +171 272 0899<BR>

</FONT>

<P>

<U><B><FONT SIZE=2>The Ministerial Conference in Singapore and

the Developing Countries</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2> An Introduction</FONT></U><FONT SIZE=2>

by Myriam vander Stichele. <I>An introduction to the World Trade

Organisation for NGOs with details on a selection of important

developmental issues to be discussed at the forthcoming WTO Ministerial

