<TITLE>ASIA-CHINA/DENG: Long Shadow Casts Over The East, West and South</TITLE>
<meta date 1997-02-20-09-07-00>
<meta category IP>
<meta code AP IP>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000080">







