 Scotland Police Ceilidh Band, listeners heard an amazing Children's Choir some 400 strong, taken from local schools, and special guest Justin Hayward from the Moody Blues. <p>           <hr>©Copyright: UNICEF 1996<hr><center><SMALL><b> [<ahref="index.html" target="_parent"> UNICEF Home Page</A>] [<ahref="http://www.childrenfirst.org">Support UNICEF</A>] [<ahref="news.html">News</A>] [<ahref="events.html">Events</A>] [<ahref="publications.html">Publications</A>] [<ahref="education.html">Education</A>]</font></SMALL></b></center></body></html>
