<html><head><title>Rwanda: Special Report - Videos</title><!!keys: ></head><body><center><h2><font size=+3>R</font>WANDA: <font size=+3>S</font>PECIAL <font size=+3>R</font>EPORT </h2></center><img src="../owo_logos/online_logochrwandsp_line.gif"> <p><p><h1>Video: Rwanda -- One Year On</h1><img width=160 height=142 src="../unicef/unicef_pix/rw_prisonboy2.gif"><br><i>"They said I have killed somebody. I haven't killed anybody..."</i><p>A 16-minute video by Unicef, consisting of four short segments. They convey at least an impression of the atmosphere in Rwanda. Please click on the name of each segment to call up a brief description and picture set of video stills:  <ul><li><a href= "chrwanda_reuniting.html">Re-uniting families</a><li><a href= "chrwanda_prisonboy.html">Children in prison</a><li><a href= "chrwanda_healing.html">Healing the mind</a><li><a href= "chrwanda_schoolbox.html">School in a box</a><p></ul><h2>Video Clips</h2>We have also selected two video clips. Although it does take time to download these clips, we found them so stirring that we felt the time delay shouldn't stop us offering them to you. <p><ul><li> The first clip is of <a href="../media/rwandaboy.mov"> a little boy accused of genocide, </a> speaking from prison. It is 10 seconds long, and may take a few minutes to download. In the whole video the footage of the children in the camps or the prisons cannot fail to move, despite the syrupy commentary. <p><li> The second clip consists of a pan across  a <a href="../media/camppan.mov"> refugee camp </a>- which made us gasp at its scale. This clip is about 15 seconds long, but still covered only a small part of the camp. As many as 200,000 people are living in Kibeho and Ndago camps.</i></ul><p><br><img src="../owo_logos/online_logochrwandsp_line.gif"> <p><h3><i>'When soldiers came and started shooting, I hid for four days. Then I walked for four days. My mother was alive then - she said "You go, I'll follow." She never made it.'   '</i> </h3></ul><p><img align=left hspace=24 vspace=20 src="../owo_logos/new_more.gif"><a href="chrwandsp_top.html"><li><b>Rwanda Special Report: Contents</a><br><li><a href="chrwandsp_maps.html">Maps </a><br><li><a href="chrwandsp_backg.html">Background</a><br><li><a href="chrwandsp_story.html">Feature stories</a><br><li><a href="chrwandsp_news.html">News<li><a href="chrwandsp_help.html">How You Can Help</a><br clear=left><p><p><img src="../owo_logos/online_logochrwandsp_line.gif"> <p></body></html>
