es International:  <a href="../crosslines/xlines16_rwanda.html">A US battle</a><br><li>AICF: <a href="../crosslines/xlines10_rwanda.html">Ineffectual and inert UN</a><br><li>CARE: <a href="../crosslines/xlines9_rwanda.html">Why co-operate?</a><br><dd><a href="../crosslines/xlines20_rwanda.html">Germany criticized for poor planning</a><br><li>WHO: <a href="../crosslines/xlines7_rwanda.html">A critical look</a><br><li><a href="../crosslines/xlines17_rwanda.html">The famine business</a><br><li><a href="../crosslines/xlines5_rwanda.html">Relief for the relievers</a><br><li><a href="../crosslines/xlines13_rwanda.html">Radios for Rwanda</a><br><p><br></ul></ul><img src="../owo_logos/online_logochrwandsp_line.gif"> <p><h3><i>'Half of the children don't think they'll live to be adults. Their sense of future is gone - so forgiveness seems intangible to them.' </i> </h3><p><br><img align=left hspace=24 vspace=20 src="../owo_pix/new_more.gif"><a href="chrwandsp_top.html"><li><b>Rwanda Special Report: Contents</a><br><li><a href="chrwandsp_maps.html">Maps </a><br><li><a href="chrwandsp_vid.html">Photographs and video clips</a><br><li><a href="chrwandsp_backg.html">Background</a><br><li><a href="chrwandsp_news.html">News</a><li><a href="chrwandsp_help.html">How You Can Help</a><br clear=left><p><p><img src="../owo_logos/online_logochrwandsp_line.gif"> <p></body></html>
