<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/euforic/courier/159e_kar.htm 193.128.6.150 19970222013041 text/html 15235
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 22 Feb 1997 01:30:16 GMT
