<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT17-B18-242</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000576-B038-104</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/euforic/planete/33timmer.htm 193.128.6.150 19970213141853 text/html 15238
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
